ly sexy older woman with him..."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Charlie"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[2]...How's it goin' with Shino-chan lately? I didn't wanna come off as"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["thoughtless last time so I didn't say much but, I can't help but worry 'bout my friends."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Charlie"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[16-nb]Our school lives are gonna be over before ye know it, get to doin' whatcha gotta do."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Charlie"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[21-nb]It's pointless to look at girls through yer personal rose tinted glasses,"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["ya know. Everyone's actually pretty sex minded, so try yer best."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Charlie"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[17-nb]Heh, don't mind me, I'm just gettin' into this by myself. Soz soz♪"]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["It's pretty insane how convincing it sounds coming from him."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["He's got a point too, maybe I'm just pushing that sort of an image onto"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Shino, she herself might be surprisingly down for it."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Charlie"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[2]I mean, I went outta my way to... nah, nevermind. That really would be"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["too much. I think I went a step too far?"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Charlie"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[7]\\SM[double]Well, let's both have a good time, aight? See ya~"]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameter